Marketing Analytics Synthetic Dataset (Portfolio-ready)
Files generated:
- customers.csv: customer_id, full_name, gender, age, segment, city, province, join_date
- products.csv: product_id, product_name, category, brand, unit_price, cost
- transactions.csv: transaction_id, transaction_date, customer_id, product_id, quantity, unit_price, amount, channel, campaign_id, city, province
- campaigns.csv: campaign_id, campaign_name, channel, start_date, end_date
- marketing_spend.csv: campaign_id, month, region, spend, impressions, clicks, conversions
- targets.csv: month, region, sales_target

Dataset span: Jan 2023 - Dec 2024. Transactions: 50k rows. Customers: 3k. Products: 150. Campaigns: 40.
Purpose: Designed for marketing performance analysis, ROI, customer segmentation, anomaly detection, and building dashboards (Power BI / Tableau).
